snippet.title: Element X Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1361120/Element_X/

Aerobox Games has released their first game! Element X, a roguelite, bullet hell! Official release is October 9th on Steam

Element X Website:
- https://aeroboxgames.com/

Video Edited by JLoad 
- twitter: https://twitter.com/Jebailey97
